@startuml Recruiter_Applications

title Recruiter - Applications (Module D)

actor Recruiter as "👔 Nhà Tuyển Dụng"

rectangle "APPLICATIONS" {
    usecase "List Applications\nfor My Jobs" as D3
    usecase "View Application\nDetails" as D4
    usecase "Update Application\nStatus" as D5
    usecase "Reject\nApplication" as D6
    usecase "Download CV\nSnapshot" as D7
    usecase "View Status\nHistory" as D8
}

Recruiter --> D3: 1. View applications
D3 --> D4: 2. View details
D4 --> D5: 3. Update status
D4 --> D6: 4. Reject application
D4 --> D7: 5. Download CV
D4 --> D8: 6. View status history

note right of D3
  **Priority:** P0 (Critical)
  **Status:** Implemented ✅
end note

@enduml
